Sales Tribune:
its an app that is going to feature sales reps in the door to door industry/Sales. It'll be something similar to the Players Tribune for sports.

this app will feature one on one interview/stories with selected reps telling stories of there success, trials, advice, and etc.

the app will have a video of the interview/stories and the text from it.


